<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655000' id='t-655000'>So, that was the result. It was Mike,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657000' id='t-657000'>the first thermonuclear bomb, in 1952.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>That was designed on that machine,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662000' id='t-662000'>in the woods behind the Institute.</span>
