<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664000' id='t-664000'>So Von Neumann invited a whole gang of weirdos</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668000' id='t-668000'>from all over the world to work on all these problems.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671000' id='t-671000'>Barricelli, he came to do what we now call, really, artificial life,</span>
