<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684000' id='t-684000'>Trying to start an artificial genetic system running in the computer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689000' id='t-689000'>Began -- his universe started March 3, '53.</span>
